"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-25-rafael-nadal-faces-paris-olympics-nightmare-new-thigh-injury-21297820\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Rafael Nadal has suffered a new thigh injury and has been seen with a bandage on his leg, leading him to cancel practice withAlexander Zverevahead of theOlympic GamesinParis, amid speculation he could withdraw.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not yet known how severe Nadal's thigh problem is - but given hislong-term injury issuesover the last few years - it is a big concern for the 38-year-old, who is due to be playing his first-round singles and doubles matches this weekend.\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.9459767351419442e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-time major winner, famously known as the King of Clay,faces Hungary's Marton Fucsovicsin his opening singles match and is projected to play his rivalNovak Djokovicin a blockbuster second-round showdown at Roland-Garros.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.998893793584032, \"rank\": 0.0011056973880467396, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marton,_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.8493083334441812, \"rank\": 0.09385219097447657, \"text\": \"Marton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marton,_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marton,_New_Zealand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, playing his last Olympics, has also formed a Spanish dream team with Wimbledon championCarlos Alcarazand they are set to lock horns with Argentine duo Maximo Gonzalez and Andres Molteni in their first-round match.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9855820647313082, \"rank\": 0.008937301253375095, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\", \"score\": 0.9999999983701855, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maximo Gonzalez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andr\\u00e9s_Molteni\", \"score\": 0.9999999288859297, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andres Molteni\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andr\\u00e9s_Molteni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andr\\u00e9s_Molteni\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The veteran's participation is now in doubt, though, because of his new injury, which forced him to cancel a scheduled training session with this year'sFrench Open runner-upZverev on Thursday, one day before the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadalskipped Wimbledon this yearbecause he did not want to risk injury with going from the clay surface to grass and then straight back to the red dirt.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it now appears that Nadal's hopes of avoiding injury has ultimately failed.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.9459767351419442e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic is very much hoping that Nadal will be fit to play in singles and was 'excited' by the idea of possibly facing his Big Three rival in the second round.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.9459767351419442e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am aware that an era with Nadal and [Andy] Murray's retirements after the Games is ending,' Djokovic said.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.9459767351419442e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 16